<p><a href="http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=zJGHPpN38bUC" rel="nofollow">Montaigne</a></p></div></div><div style="display: none;" id="edit_body_t1_33an"></div><div class="comment-links"><ul class="clear"><li class="first"><a id="up_t1_33an" class="up" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_33an')" >Vote up</a></li><li><a id="down_t1_33an" class="down" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_33an')" >Vote down</a></li><li><a id="permalink_t1_33an" href="http://lesswrong.com/lw/37k/rationality_quotes_december_2010/33an?c=1" class=" " target="_parent" >Permalink</a></li><li><a id="reply_a_t1_33an" class="" href="javascript:reply('t1_33an')">Reply</a></li></ul><span id=status_t1_33an class="error" style="display: none;"></span></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_33an" class="child" ><div id="siteTable_t1_33an" class="sitetable"><div id="ajaxHook_t1_33an" class="ajaxhook"></div><div id="thingrow_t1_33cz" class="comment" ><div id="pre_t1_33cz" class="parent"><a name="33cz" ></a></div><div id="entry_t1_33cz" class="entry"><div id="collapsed_t1_33cz" class="comment-meta collapsed clear " style='display:none'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author gray"><a id="author_t1_33cz" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/shokwave/">shokwave</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">08 December 2010 03:18:14PM</span><span class="votes " >2 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_33cz'] = ['1 point', '2 points', '3 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return showcomment('t1_33cz')">[+] (0 children)</a></div><div id="display_t1_33cz" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_33cz" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/shokwave/">shokwave</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">08 December 2010 03:18:14PM</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_33cz'>2 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_33cz'] = ['1 point', '2 points', '3 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_33cz')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_33cz" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><p>Strikes a blow against education as the source of reason, but also strikes a blow against reason requiring training. Ambivalent.</p></div></div><div style="display: none;" id="edit_body_t1_33cz"></div><div class="comment-links"><ul class="clear"><li class="first"><a id="up_t1_33cz" class="up" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_33cz')" >Vote up</a></li><li><a id="down_t1_33cz" class="down" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_33cz')" >Vote down</a></li><li><a id="permalink_t1_33cz" href="http://lesswrong.com/lw/37k/rationality_quotes_december_2010/33cz?c=1" class=" " target="_parent" >Permalink</a></li><li><a id="parent_t1_33cz" href="#33an" class="bylink">Parent</a></li><li><a id="reply_a_t1_33cz" class="" href="javascript:reply('t1_33cz')">Reply</a></li></ul><span id=status_t1_33cz class="error" style="display: none;"></span></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_33cz" class="child" ></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div><div id="thingrow_t1_332p" class="comment" ><div id="pre_t1_332p" class="parent"><a name="332p" ></a></div><div id="entry_t1_332p" class="entry"><div id="collapsed_t1_332p" class="comment-meta collapsed clear " style='display:none'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author gray"><a id="author_t1_332p" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/sfb/">sfb</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">07 December 2010 05:52:51PM</span><span class="votes " >6 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_332p'] = ['5 points', '6 points', '7 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return showcomment('t1_332p')">[+] (0 children)</a></div><div id="display_t1_332p" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comm