="up" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_3276')" >Vote up</a></li><li><a id="down_t1_3276" class="down" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_3276')" >Vote down</a></li><li><a id="permalink_t1_3276" href="http://lesswrong.com/lw/37k/rationality_quotes_december_2010/3276?c=1" class=" " target="_parent" >Permalink</a></li><li><a id="reply_a_t1_3276" class="" href="javascript:reply('t1_3276')">Reply</a></li></ul><span id=status_t1_3276 class="error" style="display: none;"></span></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_3276" class="child" ><div id="siteTable_t1_3276" class="sitetable"><div id="ajaxHook_t1_3276" class="ajaxhook"></div><div id="thingrow_t1_3377" class="comment" ><div id="pre_t1_3377" class="parent"><a name="3377" ></a></div><div id="entry_t1_3377" class="entry"><div id="collapsed_t1_3377" class="comment-meta collapsed clear " style='display:none'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author gray"><a id="author_t1_3377" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/JoshuaZ/">JoshuaZ</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">08 December 2010 02:56:30AM</span><span class="votes " >1 point</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_3377'] = ['0 points', '1 point', '2 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return showcomment('t1_3377')">[+] (1 child)</a></div><div id="display_t1_3377" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_3377" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/JoshuaZ/">JoshuaZ</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">08 December 2010 02:56:30AM</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_3377'>1 point</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_3377'] = ['0 points', '1 point', '2 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_3377')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_3377" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><p>This may be funny but the actual context  makes it a) less rationalist and b) a bit sad. There's some argument that he was actually talking about the standard at the time that Jews couldn't have any access to the trendier clubs.</p></div></div><div style="display: none;" id="edit_body_t1_3377"></div><div class="comment-links"><ul class="clear"><li class="first"><a id="up_t1_3377" class="up" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_3377')" >Vote up</a></li><li><a id="down_t1_3377" class="down" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_3377')" >Vote down</a></li><li><a id="permalink_t1_3377" href="http://lesswrong.com/lw/37k/rationality_quotes_december_2010/3377?c=1" class=" " target="_parent" >Permalink</a></li><li><a id="parent_t1_3377" href="#3276" class="bylink">Parent</a></li><li><a id="reply_a_t1_3377" class="" href="javascript:reply('t1_3377')">Reply</a></li></ul><span id=status_t1_3377 class="error" style="display: none;"></span></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_3377" class="child" ><div id="siteTable_t1_3377" class="sitetable"><div id="ajaxHook_t1_3377" class="ajaxhook"></div><div id="thingrow_t1_34mg" class="comment" ><div id="pre_t1_34mg" class="parent"><a name="34mg" ></a></div><div id="entry_t1_34mg" class="entry"><div id="collapsed_t1_34mg" class="comment-meta collapsed clear " style='display:none'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author gray"><a id="author_t1_34mg" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/Miller/">Miller</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">11 December 2010 04:59:36PM<em>*</em>&nbsp;</span><span class="votes " >1 point</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_34mg'] = ['0 points', '1 point', '2 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return showcomment('t1_34mg')">[+] (0 children)</a></div><div id="display_t1_34mg" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_34mg" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/Miller/">Miller</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">11 December 2010 04:59:36PM<em>*</em>&nbsp;</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_34mg'>1 point</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_34mg'] = ['0 points', '1 point', '2 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_34mg')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_34mg" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><p>Interesting -- below I give the wikipedia take on it.</p>

<blockquote>
  <p><a href="http://en.wikiquote.org/wiki/Groucho_Marx" rel="nofollow">http://en.wikiquote.org/wiki/Groucho_Marx</a></p>
  
  <p>I sent the club a wire stating, "PLEASE ACCEPT MY RESIGNATION. I DON'T WANT TO BELONG TO ANY CLUB THAT WILL ACCEPT PEOPLE LIKE ME AS A MEMBER".</p>
  
  <p>Telegram to the Friar's Club of Beverly Hills to which he belonged, as recounted in Groucho and Me (1959), p. 321</p>
</blockquote>

<p>Groucho sent the quote to a club which he was a member of, that was founded by a Jew. I can see how one could infer an ironic reference to antisemitism from that. Interesting that the quote as often paraphrased drops the 'people like me' part.</p></div></div><div style="display: none;" id="edit_body_t1_34mg"></div><div class="comment-links"><ul class="clear"><li class="first"><a id="up_t1_34mg" class="up" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_34mg')" >Vote up</a></li><li><a id="down_t1_34mg" class="down" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_34mg')" >Vote down</a></li><li><a id="permalink_t1_34mg" href="http://lesswrong.com/lw/37k/rationality_quotes_december_2010/34mg?c=1" class=" " target="_parent" >Permalink</a></li><li><a id="parent_t1_34mg" href="#3377" class="bylink">Parent</a></li><li><a id="reply_a_t1_34mg" class="" href="javascript:reply('t1_34mg')">Reply</a></li></ul><span id=status_t1_34mg class="error" style="display: none;"></span></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_34mg" class="child" ></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div><div id="thingrow_t1_336u" class="comment" ><div id="pre_t1_336u" class="parent"><a name="336u" ></a></div><div id="entry_t1_336u" class="entry"><div id="collapsed_t1_336u" class="comment-meta collapsed clear " style='display:none'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author gray"><a id="author_t1_336u" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/simplicio/">simplicio</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">08 December 2010 01:44:29AM</span><span class="votes " >1 point</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_336u'] = ['0 points', '1 point', '2 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return showcomment('t1_336u')">[+] (1 child)</a></div><div id="display_t1_336u" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span