')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_327v" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><p>Pretty close to Lakein's Question: "<em>What is the best use of my time right now?</em>" (from Alan Lakein's <em>How to Get Control of Your Time and Your Life</em>, 1973).</p></div></div><div style="display: none;" id="edit_body_t1_327v"></div><div class="comment-links"><ul class="clear"><li class="first"><a id="up_t1_327v" class="up" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_327v')" >Vote up</a></li><li><a id="down_t1_327v" class="down" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_327v')" >Vote down</a></li><li><a id="permalink_t1_327v" href="http://lesswrong.com/lw/37k/rationality_quotes_december_2010/327v?c=1" class=" " target="_parent" >Permalink</a></li><li><a id="parent_t1_327v" href="#31w7" class="bylink">Parent</a></li><li><a id="reply_a_t1_327v" class="" href="javascript:reply('t1_327v')">Reply</a></li></ul><span id=status_t1_327v class="error" style="display: none;"></span></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_327v" class="child" ></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div><div id="thingrow_t1_3225" class="comment" ><div id="pre_t1_3225" class="parent"><a name="3225" ></a></div><div id="entry_t1_3225" class="entry"><div id="collapsed_t1_3225" class="comment-meta collapsed clear " style='display:none'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author gray"><a id="author_t1_3225" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/Tiiba/">Tiiba</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">03 December 2010 06:46:28PM</span><span class="votes " >10 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_3225'] = ['9 points', '10 points', '11 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return showcomment('t1_3225')">[+] (6 children)</a></div><div id="display_t1_3225" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_3225" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/Tiiba/">Tiiba</a></span