div><div id="body_t1_324d" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><p>Up voted, although I think 'wasted' is a bit harsh. I would call lost time to unsuccessful research a necessary cost. If we all knew exactly which problems to study and which approaches to use it wouldn't be research, it would be divination.</p></div></div><div style="display: none;" id="edit_body_t1_324d"></div><div class="comment-links"><ul class="clear"><li class="first"><a id="up_t1_324d" class="up" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_324d')" >Vote up</a></li><li><a id="down_t1_324d" class="down" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_324d')" >Vote down</a></li><li><a id="permalink_t1_324d" href="http://lesswrong.com/lw/37k/rationality_quotes_december_2010/324d?c=1" class=" " target="_parent" >Permalink</a></li><li><a id="parent_t1_324d" href="#31x6" class="bylink">Parent</a></li><li><a id="reply_a_t1_324d" class="" href="javascript:reply('t1_324d')">Reply</a></li></ul><span id=status_t1_324d class="error" style="display: none;"></span></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_324d" class="child" ><div id="siteTable_t1_324d" class="sitetable"><div id="ajaxHook_t1_324d" class="ajaxhook"></div><div id="thingrow_t1_3273" class="comment" ><div id="pre_t1_3273" class="parent"><a name="3273" ></a></div><div id="entry_t1_3273" class="entry"><div id="collapsed_t1_3273" class="comment-meta collapsed clear " style='display:none'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author gray"><a id="author_t1_3273" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/anonym/">anonym</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">04 December 2010 04:19:56AM</span><span class="votes " >3 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_3273'] = ['2 points', '3 points', '4 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return showcomment('t1_3273')">[+] (0 children)</a></div><div id="display_t1_3273" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_3273"